It's been dead for a while even though there's many subscribed.  I still fletch as well, skill stopped around 176. I usually only make class 2 150 range arrows for normal use and the 4 damage 125/150 range magic arrows for special occasions and the higher level rangers in my guild. I don't usually make bows, except Trueshots to sell to a guild mate who uses them to sell Raincallers (if anyone on Tarew Marr needs a raincaller, give a tell to Ziiv).
 
I recently picked up a cocatrice beak in The Overthere that has a graphic of an arrow point but have yet to attempt to do something with it. Has anything new been confirmed?
 
Lendl Wildeblade
39 Ranger, Tarew Marr
